Description: RIAA phono preamp equalization LADSPA plugin
 RIAA phono preamp equalization plugin for vinyl playback with optional
 subsonic filtering. Provides LADSPA plugin format.
 .
 Features:
  - RIAA Equalization for accurate vinyl playback
  - Optional subsonic filter (1st or 2nd order highpass at 20Hz)
  - Adjustable gain control (-40dB to +40dB)
  - Optional declick for click/pop removal
  - Optional notch filter for mains hum removal
  - Configuration file support for default settings
  - Command-line utility for batch processing
  - Supports multiple sample rates (44.1, 48, 88.2, 96, 176.4, 192 kHz)
